 
<p>

Republicans have, for years, pushed to <a href="https://www.exposedbycmd.org/2022/07/31/voters-have-no-role-to-play-in-the-rights-vision-of-a-constitutional-convention/">start a constitutional convention</a>
that would rewrite the US Constitution.  It turns out that Republicans would
have pre-imposed control of that convention, and could do whatever they wish,
disregarding the public.

 